sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant LFSR as LFSR (Edge N)
    participant FUB_IN as FUB input flop (Edge N+1)
    participant COMB as Combinational logic
    participant FUB_OUT as FUB output flop (Edge N+2)
    participant PAD as Top-level port

    LFSR->>FUB_IN: r_lfsr captured at edge N
    Note right of FUB_IN: 1 clock period
    FUB_IN->>COMB: drive combinational
    COMB->>FUB_OUT: settle within period
    Note right of FUB_OUT: edge N+2 -- this is the path STA reports
    FUB_OUT->>PAD: routed to output port
